description:
&lt;p&gt;The Staffbank for Epsom and St Helier NHS university trust are looking for an experienced Building Surveyor/ Project manangerconversant with HTM and HBNS within an Acute Hospital environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;(Hours are 37.5 flexible but covering core hours such as 10.00-12.00 and 14.00 - 16.00)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will develop, Manage,monitor and control construction related projects for the trust, This will include Building surveying, fabric works, design, coordinating with the in-house M&amp;E team to provide a complete disign package ready for tender.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please find attached a detailed job description for more information and apply online if interested and match our requirements.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an immediate start if possible&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
